values: <center>GOD. i wish i was married to Ben KweLLer.</center>

-i dont have internet at home.
-and i'm not going to even try to get it back.
-maybe for the entire summer.

-i have summer school.
-monday through thursday i'm pretty much booked.
-painting. photo. counseling. swim.
-because i didn't feel like waiting around this summer.

-i'm not even sure if i'll have a job, at Papyrus anyway.
-maybe i can find one for friday-sunday.
-i hate knick knacks too.

-i'm going to clean out my room.
-to make space.
-but i'm not sure whether to have a garage sale, or just give it all to goodwill.
-wish i could sell stuff to my friends.
-even though i'd feel guilty about charging you.
-think of all the effort.

-i miss Miranda. 
-and i'm not even sure why.

-i've been dreaming in color lately. 
-brighter than ever before. 
-i see paintings and beautiful shapes suspended in the sky.
-when i wake up i want to put it all on paper.
-but i dont have those colors in my plastic boxes.

-victor is on a business trip.
-the house is peaceful and quiet.
-i wake up early, and go to bed late.

-i thought long and hard about something.
-and i'm never going to throw a fucking party at my house ever again.
-never.
-why would i want to be insulted again?

-marcus re-formatted my computer.
-i haven't touched it since.

-goodbye LJ.
-and LJ aquaintances.

so the a/c stays off all day. and on all night. 

is it just me... or should that be the other way around?!

BILL! (Snake Charmer)


You're Bill! I love you! Anyways, you're skilled in the art of manipulation. You're very strong, talented, powerful, and witty. You don't seem to have any real sense of morality, and you only let your kindness show around a select handful of people (mostly Kiddo and B.B). You do have some regret for the horrible things you've done, but won't let it interefere with your life. You respect your opponents, and you generally believe in fair game.

Kill Bill: Which Deadly Viper Assassin Are You? (Vol. II spoilers... results with pics)

I want everyone who reads this to ask me 3 questions, no more no less. Even if you are a non-LJ user and must post anonymously. Ask me anything you want. 

Then I want you to go to your journal, copy and paste this allowing your friends (including myself) to ask you anything.

I would like to add even if you are a user there is the option to post anonymously.

i'm so bored of wastin' my time... i shall be making a disapearance. its in your hands now. ...

is it logical to think that vegetarians, or health nuts, or those raw food eaters poop less than all of the rest of us who eat anything thats thrown in front of our faces? i'm not asking if they poop less frequently, but of the mass itself. i know, i'm sick! i'm awful! i'm disgusting. but HEY! almost everything they eat has some kind of important nutritional value therefore their bodies would absorb most of the food that comes into their precious temples. soooo, that would mean less waste. wouldn't it?
i'll be away for a couple days

i'm gonna try and cancel aol today. again. not sure whether they'll give me more free internet access this time. we'll see! the doctor's visit was fine yesterday. he looked up my nose with that pokey flashlight aparatus, and having no boogies is a good thing. he asked if the ringing in my ears was any better since the last visit, i says no, and then i was suddenly lined up for third appointment on monday. acute frequency hearing loss may be the problem. i'm fucked if i don't have a job, and i'm fucked if i don't have enough hours. no one seems to mind putting in their own two cents on the subject. i'm not going to tell you how many hours you need. and i'm sure as hell not going to tell you to get a life. FUCK YOU ALL. again. good day and God bless.

hey. i dig eyebrows. especially mine.
